id: pm-v1yo
title: "GH-585: extension alias collision diagnostics for core command groups"
description: "GitHub issue #585 reports that an exporter alias can silently graft package subcommands onto an existing core command group, demonstrated by the published pm-graph extension colliding with the new core pm graph group."
type: Issue
status: in_progress
priority: 1
tags[3]: agent-ux,extensions,github
created_at: "2026-07-18T07:14:14.667Z"
updated_at: "2026-07-18T11:37:36.849Z"
assignee: maintainer-agent
author: codex-sdk-vcs-20260718
estimated_minutes: 240
acceptance_criteria: "Extension activation detects command-group and flattened-alias collisions before dispatch, emits an actionable diagnostic naming both owners, and preserves non-colliding extension commands with contract and installed-package regression coverage."
parent: pm-usfg
risk: medium
confidence: high
